進裁判室交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，巴塞迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。巴塞迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。"},{"pid":"add7c601822796eaf11e5829c46ae075f7686d51","tid":148752,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T21:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你追到打和先嘈啦<br />\n仲輸緊兩粒嘈條春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘈得未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586d35123f92bc3d3f9e8361d3878741768f11ba","tid":148752,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T21:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24GZp73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24GZp73.jpg&h=b17714ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下次樓主記得轉acc先好講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b2579fff8bb6f98ca43276a8055bd69c377643","tid":148752,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T21:42:56.000Z","msg":"幫你推幫你出名幫你紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155cd6c4f1dd440a65ec5ea4ac5296372012096b","tid":148752,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T21:43:16.000Z","msg":"用分身引戰好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}